---
title: Hot Honey Chicken Cutlet with Roasted Sesame Carrots & Cilantro Lime Rice
description: Dreaming about dinner? How about succulent pork filet, roasted sesame carrots, and fluffy cilantro lime rice? To finish things off, the pork is drizzled in a lick-the-plate-worthy sauce made with sesame oil, scallions, ginger, and honey. Talk about a dream come true!
